# clients
There are different types of clients:
- users (small stake)
- validators (large stake)
- moderator / observer (no stake)

# client functionality
- User and validator: generate, gossip, and validate event blocks
- Moderator and observer: gossip (download) and post-validate event blocks

# documentation
See Technical report at
StairDag: Cross-DAG Validation For Scalable BFT Consensus
https://arxiv.org/pdf/1908.11810.pdf